description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – review the latest headlines around the league including Kirk Cousins being named the Redskins starter over RGIII. Plus, Preseason Week 3 takeaways & the “Power Poll” debuts.
